<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">śakābtam 41<unclear>6</unclear><unclear>8</unclear></hi><note n="443-1">The symbol for thousand has been engraved after the symbol for 4 by mistake and the symbol for 6 is very faintly engraved above the symbols for 100 and 10. The last symbol for 8 is also not well formed.</note> <hi rend="grantha">mē<unclear>la</unclear></hi> <seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">pa</seg><hi rend="grantha">rābhava</hi> <seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">varuṣam</seg> <hi rend="grantha"><unclear>śrī</unclear>raṅgadēvaśikhāmaṇi tātācā</hi>
